</div>

<div class="row" id="fees">
  <div class="col-sm-12">
    <h1>Fees</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-1">
    <div class="left-header">
      <h2>Flexible</h2>
    </div>
      <p>We make it easy to understand our payments--we get paid a simple percentage
      of revenue. If your business is like most, you will have ups and downs.
      With our business model, our fate is tied to yours, and thus we do everything
      in our power to make sure your business succeeds.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-1">
    <div class="left-header">
      <h2>Paid with Proof</h2>
    </div>
    <p>We send a bill once a month--along with your monthly financials. It's easy
    that way, because you have tangible proof of the work we've done. If you don't
    get monthly financials, you don't get a bill--it's as simple as that.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3">
    <div class="left-header">
      <h2>Rates</h2>
    </div>
    <p>We put together a custom quote for you, but our rates typically fall around
      <strong>3% to 4% of revenue.</strong></p>
    <p>For example, a small business that does $200,000 per year in revenue would
      pay us only 6-8 thousand dollars for all of the above services--or approximately one
      month's pay for a skilled office manager.</p>
  </div>
</div>
